1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Not even the drinks I had were any good, as all were either flat, moldy, or thickened

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:07,520
into a goo that twitched if touched.

3
00:00:07,520 --> 00:00:12,480
The only thing I found that was somewhat ingestible was some bottles of wine I had stored for

4
00:00:12,480 --> 00:00:14,880
my wives and my date night.

5
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:17,840
That same night those things showed up in the night.

6
00:00:17,840 --> 00:00:22,840
That same night I woke up to my wife, pale with a permanent scream face now rigged in place

7
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,320
forever, getting drunk wasn't exactly my plan, but I've got to drink something.

8
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:34,400
I'd receive hell from my wife in heaven if I were to die now, especially from dehydration.

9
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:39,920
Avenging her is my only reason for going on, and I intend on doing just that.

10
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:41,440
I hear something.

11
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:42,800
I was right.

12
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:43,800
They're up there.

13
00:00:43,800 --> 00:00:45,240
I'll update again later.

14
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,400
I'm going to do some prepping.
